data.description: Welcome to 5750 Marsh Landing Dr, a pictures nestled in the heart of Winter Haven, FL. This enchanting 5-bedroom, 3-bathroom home offers a unique blend of serene lakeside living and modern comforts.Breathtaking Lake Views: Enjoy mesmerizing sunrises and tranquility evenings from your backyard as the sun glistens on the sparkling waters.Spacious Outdoor Oasis: The expansive backyard provides ample space for outdoor gatherings, gardening, and lakeside relaxation.  Thoughtful Layout: The open-concept design seamlessly connects the living, dining, and kitchen areas, creating an inviting atmosphere for both everyday living and entertaining.Private Retreat: The primary bedroom offers a peaceful escape with an ensuite bathroom and serene views of the lake.Convenient Location: Situated in a quiet neighborhood, you'll have easy access to local amenities, schools, and parks  Whether you're looking for a year-round residence or a vacation getaway, this home is a sanctuary of relaxation and natural beauty. Don't miss your chance to own this slice of paradise! Schedule a viewing today and experience the magic of lakeside living.    Several lakes with public boat ramps close by. Lake Hamilton has 2,184 acres. Lake Fannie 802 acres. Fantastic for boating and taking out a Jeski. Under 30 minutes to legoland and less than an hour to Disney World.
